sections.number: 35A.03.001 - Actions subject to review by boundary review bo
sections.text:
RCW 35A.03.001

Actions subject to review by boundary review board.

Actions taken under chapter 35A.03 RCW may be subject to potential review by a boundary review board under chapter 36.93 RCW.

Actions taken under chapter 35A.03 RCW may be subject to potential review by a boundary review board under chapter 36.93 RCW.

[ 1989 c 84 s 36.]

sections.number: 35A.03.005 - Incorporation to be governed by chapter 35.02 R
sections.text:
RCW 35A.03.005

Incorporation to be governed by chapter 35.02 RCW.

Noncharter code cities shall be incorporated as provided in chapter 35.02 RCW.

Noncharter code cities shall be incorporated as provided in chapter 35.02 RCW.

[ 1986 c 234 s 36.]
